rComments: Midterm was not hard but his finals are pretty difficult and if you don't have a high term marks before taking the final exam, you might get curved down a lot, also this prof never curves marks so it all depends on you.

Professor KK delivers super organized and clear lectures. Although this course is very hard in content, but the professor teaches it in a very inspirational way. So if you attend lectures and read most readings he posted, you will learn a lot from this course. Furthermore, assignments are hard but very enlightening, so are the test and exam.
Lecture notes are hard to follow and the course seems bird but then he curved everyone down more than 10% on the final as a result. Avoid him
